'''Jeff Quick''' is an Expo award-winning role-playing game designer. He was formerly the Senior Editor of ''[[Star Wars Gamer]]'' Magazine, as well as the Editor-in-Chief of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]''. At Samford University where he attended college for his undergraduate degree, his nickname was "Zippy."

